long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Unofficial job search extension for http://hasjob.co. Allows the user to quickly check if any job is listed on hasjob.co for the current website.

Source code available at https://github.com/HemantPawar/hasjob-extension
